Package: aaSimulator
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Axis and Allies Battles
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Edvin Fuglebakk
Maintainer: Edvin Fuglebakk <Edvin.Fuglebakk@gmail.com>
Description: package for simulating Axis and Allies battles and visualising the distribution of outcomes.
    Contains generic engine for simulating battles and plotting results, for a set order of loss specification.
    The engine is utilized by implementing a battle-function encoding the rule of the specific Axis and Allies game one wants to simulate.
    An example implementation is provided for the Larry Harris Tournament Rules for Axis and Allies Revised (LHTR 2.0). Technological development units are not included.
License: LGPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Import: data.table, ggplot2
